      "content": "but i don't really want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i don't have to. it's so expensive and stressful. if it really is just a blood clot or something from sitting too long, wouldn't an aspirin help thin the blood out? i've heard people do that for it. is it really that urgent if i can just sleep it off for a few hours and see if it's better in the morning?",
